* The client apps use this callback to return their ExampleStoreIterator implementation to the
     * federated training service.

methods.name: void onStartQuerySuccess(@NonNull ExampleStoreIterator iterator)
methods.comment: Called when the iterator is ready for use.

methods.name: void onStartQueryFailure(int errorCode)
methods.comment: Called when an error occurred and the iterator cannot be created.
